sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    participant User as Consumer
    participant App as Bill Buddy App
    participant ADR as ADR Backend
    participant Register as CDR Register
    participant Bank as Data Holder (Bank)

    %% Initial Setup (One-time)
    Note over ADR,Register: Initial Registration (One-time)
    ADR->>Register: Register as ADR (ACCC accreditation)
    Register-->>ADR: ADR credentials & certificates
    ADR->>Bank: Dynamic Client Registration
    Bank-->>ADR: Client ID for this Data Holder

    %% Consumer Initiates Connection
    Note over User,Bank: Consumer Consent Flow
    User->>App: "Connect my bank account"
    App->>ADR: Initiate connection request
    ADR->>Register: Get Data Holder endpoints
    Register-->>ADR: Bank's authorization/token URLs
    
    ADR->>Bank: Pushed Authorization Request (PAR)
    Bank-->>ADR: request_uri
    
    ADR->>App: Redirect URL with request_uri
    App->>User: Redirect to bank login
    User->>Bank: Authenticate (username/password/MFA)
    Bank->>User: Show consent screen
    User->>Bank: Grant consent
    Bank->>App: Redirect with authorization code
    App->>ADR: Forward authorization code

    %% Token Exchange
    Note over ADR,Bank: Token Exchange (mTLS secured)
    ADR->>Bank: Exchange code for tokens (POST /token)
    Bank-->>ADR: access_token + refresh_token + id_token
    ADR->>ADR: Store tokens securely

    %% Data Retrieval
    Note over ADR,Bank: Data Retrieval
    ADR->>Bank: GET /banking/accounts
    Bank-->>ADR: Account list (BSBs, balances)
    
    ADR->>Bank: GET /banking/accounts/{id}/transactions
    Bank-->>ADR: Transaction history
    
    ADR->>Bank: GET /banking/accounts/{id}/direct-debits
    Bank-->>ADR: Scheduled payments & direct debits

    %% Data Processing
    Note over App,ADR: Data Processing
    ADR->>ADR: Store in CDR data environment
    ADR->>ADR: ML categorisation (subscriptions, bills)
    ADR->>App: Processed data + insights
    App->>User: "Found 12 subscriptions, $847/month"

    %% Ongoing Access
    Note over ADR,Bank: Ongoing Data Refresh
    loop Every few hours / on-demand
        ADR->>Bank: GET /banking/accounts/{id}/transactions
        Bank-->>ADR: New transactions
        ADR->>App: Push updates
    end

    %% Consent Withdrawal
    Note over User,Bank: Consent Withdrawal (if requested)
    User->>App: "Disconnect bank"
    App->>ADR: Revoke consent
    ADR->>Bank: DELETE consent arrangement
    Bank-->>ADR: Consent revoked
    ADR->>ADR: Delete CDR data (within 7 days)
    ADR-->>App: Confirmation
    App->>User: "Bank disconnected"
